values:
Or Just ME!!!!!

I must be a magnet to the incredible stupid! Wasnt there a patron saint for these lunkheads. ST DUFUS OF THE CLUELESS. It seem s since we eliminated our customer service people, I get all the gems! First off how an upscale store that prides itself on Customer Satisfaction, eliminates the one group that is actually trained to do said satisfcation!&nbsp;&nbsp; RUTROO RASTRO!&nbsp; So now they come to me!&nbsp;

WHOS OUR FIRST CALLER?&nbsp;
WELL DR CRANK ITS SIMON.......
GO AHEAD SIMON IM SORT OF LISTENING, BUT NOT REALLY&nbsp;......you see Simon, OOHH my dear sweet simple Simon I read your file......A Polish Immigrant who decided to buy a couch, chair ottoman and love seat&nbsp; and have it delivered to your home in forest Hills, then ship it to your summer home in Fleischmanns, I HAVENT A CLUE WHER THE HELL THAT IS, but its close enough to call Bob and Doug Mackenzie neighbors, eh! So Simple Simon packs up his pies and decides that he realizes teh couch is a differnt color then everything else! I dont know maybe its wearing its winter coat now, or perhaps he should have inspected the pieces closer before he sent them up with BALTO!&nbsp; Simple simon now DEMANDS I remove the furniture, I tell him absolutely not a problem....ONCE they are back in Forest Hills. We do not deliver that far hence why he had to transport it himself! I remind him of this! He gets agitated, I explain we are not responsible for this, as he was past his&nbsp; 3 day return window by 9 months! Ohh hes undaunted, demanding i make "situation correct". Told him it would be my pleasure, as soon as the merchandise came back to wher we delivered it. We keep this lively banter on for quite a bit, back and forth.... Hes getting agitated and agitated....I quickly refer to my Customer service manual...How To deal with a Crazy Polish Immigrant who actually makes the jokes true....Ay yes Chapter five...Tell an analagy.....Simon, if you walk into a chinese food restaurant with a live chicken, and you put said chicken down in the kitchen, and then you order chowmein., you cant get made at the chef if he uses fresh chicken!....Oh boy did &nbsp;he start going off. He used the word Doopah, It means ass i believe. A few hours later I get a call that he had complained about me, called me a Bad Person, who wouldnt help him out. I was not being sympathetic to him, since he MOVED UPSTATE A MONTH AGO.... Ahh Says I, so I asked the GM what number should I call and apologize at. She gives me his home number its a 718 area code....... I stare at her balnky for a minute then laugh.....Had almost as much fun as the Chinese family that I had to deal with On Sunday after Saint Patricks day!

So I get a phone call from my Delivery gut that he is picking up a tree we sold. Yes thats right we sell $1,500 real looking fake birch trees. So I get this tree back in the store and see the top half sawed off. So Feeling that I am now on BSI...BLOOMINDALES STUPIDITY INSTIGATORS I ask the driver what happened to this tree. Mind you It is&nbsp;normally over 9 feet tall and weighs over 100&nbsp;pounds. The driver pull out his notes from NOV 16 when he delivered thsi tree and notates that the customer had asked him to cut it down so it would fit in his Hovel! Well Thank you MATLOCk, case closed NO MONEY BACK.....so i go upstairs a tune on my lips and a skip to my step and tell the Store Manager to deny the&nbsp;credit....

Hey Abbot whos on first.... I DONT KNOW..Third base............&nbsp; She blinks and says that I must be confused and she had promised&nbsp;ANOTHER &nbsp;customer a refund beacuse we delivered a broken tree.&nbsp; I ask her How mnay incredibly real looking Fake 9 foot Birch trees in grecian urns we could have possibly sold in the past year.....WAIT FOR IT...One i reply, I invetoried evrey one of those ridculous mother fucking shrubs and could to the instant point out where all of THEM where....&nbsp;

Well now IM PISSED....So i have some other trees taking up space in my back office areas........so i take my favorite hammer to the grecian urns and give them a good whack.....This is called SALVAGING which means we Put them in teh trash compactor and give them no resale. MOral of teh story I tuen to my stock crew and tell them I CAN JUST AS EASILY SALVAGE THEIR ASSES! They worked realyy good the rest of&nbsp; the day......

YOU HAVE GOT TO BE SHITING ME!!!!!!!!!!&nbsp;

No excuses please. Not interested in sidebars or stories.............................

I made a commitment to do something and I will do it. I will be going on as Max this weekend in Sound of Music and It scares me. Will I be ready, I hope so. I will do my best, I will not dissapoint my cast mates, my crew and Hopefuly not the people who spend there money to see this.&nbsp; 

General note &nbsp;to all of you who think you are better then the rest of us....YOU ARENT! If you were you would be somehere else, your not.! To those who give their time, their effort ,their energy to this "community theatre" thank you! &nbsp; I wil lnever beg anyone to do a show, I dont see anyone worthy enough of that.....you dont want to be here, DONT..guess what I want you here even less then you want to be here.&nbsp;

Time to put another load in......
